{"tid":2043122,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"tg離開左個叫雞group","createTime":"2020-05-30T08:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T16:04:47.000Z","uid":3204,"like":10,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"23a9db37d992838e21d9073c89aadfcb07da9d29","tid":2043122,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T08:11:21.000Z","msg":"上年運動前後我已經開始fb/ig unfriend人<br />\n一來發現自己之前加加埋埋好多唔熟or唔識既人<br />\n二來有一少部分朋友係真係好港豬或者唔認同香港發生緊既<br />\n甚至有人走黎叫我唔好po野唔好理政治<br />\n我就一次過unfriend曬佢地<br />\n<br />\n到最近國安法立法<br />\n我都會留意下d fd po咩<br />\n就發現tg有個叫雞谷入面十幾人<br />\n一日會有2000個對話，<br />\n對國安法好似完全無關心<br />\n我琴日就忍唔住leave group<br />\n<br />\n點知佢地今日就走黎問我係咪leave左佢同埋點解<br />\n我話因為覺得佢好港豬就leave左<br />\n之後佢地就send左佢哋叫啲妓女捐錢去攬炒團隊既prove俾我(捐左5位數字HKD...)<br />\n話佢其實唔係政治冷感<br />\n只tg唔安全講政治<br />\n<br />\n如果係你地<br />\n你地會唔會接受呢個理由? <br />\n<br />\n利申: 只睇無叫過"},{"pid":"6c242228cc24714063daaecf65d5fcefa17ef93d","tid":2043122,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T08:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13de6edcdd0b74c1dd68ff41aca3dc82bb8a9111","tid":2043122,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c242228cc24714063daaecf65d5fcefa17ef93d","tid":2043122,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T08:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T08:11:54.000Z","msg":"笑西？"},{"pid":"cfe7a6b0e54f5b52b4bc054f5c2abd16807fbde8","tid":2043122,"uid":202348,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T08:13:04.000Z","msg":"叫雞同示威無衝突..."},{"pid":"8be6374420a16ba900e4faa134440478d126a852","tid":2043122,"uid":156092,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T08:14:57.000Z","msg":"闗注同叫雞 <br />\n<br />\n兩件事 <br />\n<br />\n你吊緊閪會吾會關心國安法？<br />\n<br />\nON99"},{"pid":"0c4d32fad70fca3659f18557b2b28876f713d2dd","tid":2043122,"u